Text.Value: What is happening at Moonrise Towers?
What do githyanki want with cultists?
What do you know about this 'weapon'?
Path to Moonrise Towers... Absolute... Answering the call...
Why were you so desperate to run?
Little house... Under a hill... Somewhere... Don't... Remember...
*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*
*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*
*The corpse seems willing to speak - but not to its killer.*

Synopsis: He reveals some info about the Absolute's activity at Moonrise.
